==用法==
<nowiki>{{Space|N}}</nowiki>產生連續N個不換行空格；無參數的<nowiki>{{Space}}</nowiki>只產生1個不換行空格。

:Better results can frequently be gained by using {{Tl|nowrap}} and/or the HTML formatting <code><nowiki><tt> ...</tt></nowiki></code> about any of the spacing templates, since browser design philosophy is to trim consecutive spaces, check results also in different zoom settings, and on more than one browser if possible. One repeat offender is the [[Internet Explorer|IE]] browser family... which is unfortunately the numerically predominate browser of the world by a large margin since it's embedded with most turn-key [[personal computer]] sales.

